                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for efficiently purifying chitosan through combined degradation of chitin by enzyme method and microwave assistance",
                    "一种酶法和微波辅助联合降解甲壳素高效提纯壳聚糖的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for efficiently purifying chitosan by jointly degrading chitin through an enzyme method and microwave assistance, and belongs to the technical field of chitosan production. The method comprises the following steps: washing chitin with running water until no impurity exists on the surface, air-drying at normal temperature, and crushing; adding hydrogen peroxide into the chitosan, rapidly heating and oxidizing to obtain oxidized chitosan, and cooling; adding compound protease into the mixture, and putting the mixture into a microwave reactor for reaction; heating for enzyme deactivation to obtain a crude chitosan solution; filtering the chitosan crude liquid, and washing with clear water until the pH is neutral; and drying the product at a low temperature, and putting the dried product into a supercritical carbon dioxide extractor to obtain a residual material which is purified chitosan after the extraction is completed. The chitin is subjected to enzymolysis under the microwave-assisted condition, and the crude chitosan is purified by using a supercritical carbon dioxide extraction process, so that the chitosan with relatively high extraction rate and purity is finally obtained."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种酶法和微波辅助联合降解甲壳素高效提纯壳聚糖的方法，属于壳聚糖生产技术领域。该方法为将甲壳素用流水冲洗至表面没有杂质后，常温风干，粉碎；向其中加入双氧水，迅速升温氧化，得到氧化壳聚糖，冷却；向其中加入复合蛋白酶，放入微波反应器反应；加热灭酶，得到壳聚糖粗液；将壳聚糖粗液过滤后清水冲洗至pH至中性；将产物低温烘干，放入超临界二氧化碳萃取器中，萃取完成后残留物料即为纯化后的壳聚糖。本发明甲壳素在微波辅助条件下进行酶解，并利用超临界二氧化碳萃取工艺对粗壳聚糖进行纯化，最终得到提取率和纯度均较高的壳聚糖。"
                }
            ]
